##########################################################################################################################
#                                                                                                                        #
#                     GLOBAL RESOLVED ENERGY BALANCED WITH GALACTIC COSMIC RAYS - GREB-GCR-v.0.1                         #  
#                                                                                                                        #
#                                                                                                                        # 
#   Simplified climate model inspired by the galactics cosmic rays theory and the increase in greenhouse gas emission    #   
#   on global climate system. This model was developed from the greb model code, the GREB model is available in:         #   
#   "http://users.monash.edu.au/~dietmard/content/GREB/GREB_model.html"                                                  #
#                                                                                                                        #
#   The tool GREB-GCR was developed for a doctorate thesis, available at the link below:                                 #          
#   "https://repositorio.ufrn.br/jspui/bitstream/123456789/27210/1/Simula%c3%a7%c3%b5estemperaturaar_Oliveira_2019.pdf"  #                                                                                                                  
#                                                                                                                        #
#   The model GREB-GCR has been validated and the results published in an article, read this work at the link below:     #                                                                                          
#   "https://periodicos.ufpe.br/revistas/rbgfe/article/view/236751"                                                      #
#                                                                                                                        #  
#   GREB-GCR site below:                                                                                                 #
#   "https://sites.google.com/view/klimatosfera/greb-gcr"                                                                #
#                                                                                                                        #
#   contact: emerson.oliveira@univasf.edu.br                                                                             #
#                                                                                                                        #    
#                                                                                                                        #   
